2. DATA  — files under `benchmark/` and `reference_runs/`
============================================================

The underlying federal regulatory text and public-comment text contained or
referenced in this dataset are works of the U.S. federal government and are
in the public domain.

LLM-derived annotations and structural extractions (deontic-unit
segmentation, claim extraction, claim-to-provision matches, frame labels,
stakeholder bucket assignments, and reference model outputs) are released
under the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License (CC-BY-4.0):
https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

If you use the data, please cite the accompanying paper (see CITATION.cff).
